                Health insurance is a type of coverage that provides financial protection against the high costs of medical expenses and healthcare services. It helps individuals and families manage the financial burden that can arise from unexpected illnesses, injuries, or medical treatments. Here are some reasons why you should consider buying health insurance, along with its benefits and common policy features:
            </p>
